#: aot_flask/templates/pages/function_options/conditional_options/measurement_dict.html:11
#: aot_flask/templates/pages/function_options/conditional_options/measurement_past_average.html:10
#: aot_flask/templates/pages/function_options/conditional_options/measurement_past_sum.html:6
